{
  "texts": [
    "In diversity literature, this has been operationalized as variety [59].",
    "For example, to construct a thematic profile, the distribution of dramas, comedies, westerns, etc.",
    "in festivals could be used.",
    "For operationalizing concepts with only two categories like gender diversity, percentages or ratios of counts suffice.",
    "However, we argue that using count distributions is not the best approach in most multinomial cases, as such metadata categories are typically not inherently equidistant."
  ]
}